Section 4 – Add feedback to seller

* The user logged to his account -> The function will print user’s products (from his orders array) and will ask him to choose to
which product he wants to add a feedback, the input will be a number (single char – to make an easy validation) -> Inside the chosen
product’s class the function will add the feedback to seller’s feedbacks array.


